      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so dishonest to pretend that \"small steps\" change anything. it's like being told to enjoy the view while the building is literally on fire. if the end is inevitable, why am i supposed to keep dragging myself through this misery? it feels more like just prolonging the inevitable suffering for no reason.",
